Imo minecraft is the perfect game. It has support for all input methods(controller, touch, keyboard and mouse). It supports mods via addons. Community resource packs and behavior packs make a great way to change up the game. My only slight problem is I would love a customizable hud for touch screen like some shooters on android for when playing pvp on servers
